This FULLY FURNISHED condo offers spectacular views of the Ala Wai Boat Harbor, Magic Island and the beautiful blue Pacific Ocean. Watch an endlessly entertaining array of ocean activities: surfers, paddlers, boats going out and coming in, Friday night boat races.. all from the comfort of your own lanai.
Two bedroom, two bathroom, one parking. Bedrooms are separated for privacy.
All new linens, including quality 100% cotton sheets.
Marble flooring in entry, kitchen, bathrooms and lanai, white-washed wood flooring in living room, carpet in bedrooms. Kitchen has Corian countertops and stainless steel appliances. Overall, the unit is a bit dated, but still lovely. And priced right to rent quickly.
Ala Moana Beach Park and Ala Moana Shopping Center are just steps away, and Waikiki, Kakaako and downtown Honolulu are nearby. Everything you need is within walking distance.
Enjoy resort-style amenities including a swimming pool, jacuzzi, barbecue areas, tennis courts, and 24-hour security.
